      "para_id": "Q004356.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) Šu-Suen , the powerful king , king of Urim , king of the four quarters : Aba-Enlilgin , child of Lu-Inana , the animal-fattener , is your servant ."
    }
